A, B, female from Aana Mudi Shola National Park, India (WAM T109510). A, dorsal view; B, ventral view. C–F, female from Nilgiris, Tamil Nadu, India (ZMUC 12902). C, dorsal view; D, ventral view; E, epigyne, ventral view; F, epigyne, dorsal view). Scale bar = 2.0 mm in A- D; 0.5 mm in E; 0.2 mm in F.
